title: Objects + Bounding Boxes using Resnet50-my
description: Object Detection using ImageAI - Resnet50 This is is starter kernel, mainly for learning purposes and getting started. There is so much to learn more and improve. I am using imageai package along with resnet50 pretrained model. For the baseline model, one can refer to a great kernel shared by Miha Skalic: Classifier as a bounding-box predictor
